for 150 assets:;
ram=16GB
storage500gb(depends on how often you scan your assets and reports generation.)
cpu=4 cores
before installation,
disable selinux, firewall, defender,ips/ids and assign static ip which can ping google.com
after installation of insightvm/nexpose,
if console did not open then,
systemctl stop nexposeconsole
systemctl start nexposeconsole,
go to default installation directory in linux machine i.e.
cd /opt/rapid7/nexpose
run nsc.sh script to force load the console of insightvm/nexpose
to uninstall the nexpose/insightvm 
cd /opt/rapid7/nexpose/.install4j/ and ./uninstall

note(every ip/hostname used by the insightvm/nexpose should be allowed by the network firewall)
